      <h2 class="section-title section-title-light">Brand Colors</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="doc-info doc-info-light">Contorno Brand Guidelines<br>Section 3.0: Brand Colors</div>
  </div>
  <p class="color-intro fi">Contorno's palette draws directly from the physical world of La Punta: the warm terracotta of sun-baked concrete, the deep green of jungle canopy, and the soft faded blue of the Pacific at dusk. These are not trend colors. They are the actual colors of the place.</p>
